WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:04.069
<i>Previously on</i> reign...
Francis: <i>The duke of guise,</i>
<i>your uncle, is</i>

00:04.071 --> 00:06.238
<i>A dangerously ambitious man.</i>
<i>I read your letter.</i>

00:06.240 --> 00:07.740
I wrote that letter thinking
I'd never see you again.

00:07.742 --> 00:09.608
Mary: <i>I know.</i>
<i>None of us are responsible</i>

00:09.610 --> 00:12.511
<i>For our hearts--</i>
<i>only our actions.</i>

00:12.513 --> 00:14.346
Catherine:
<i>I do read henry's bible.</i>

00:14.348 --> 00:16.749
It belonged to henry,
and henry went mad,

00:16.751 --> 00:18.350
<i>And now it belongs to you.</i>

00:18.352 --> 00:20.119
<i>You've been poisoned.</i>

00:20.121 --> 00:21.353
Antoine: <i>I think this sebastian</i>
<i>is the man</i>

00:21.355 --> 00:23.489
Responsible for
our brother's death.

00:23.491 --> 00:25.391
The ledger we found
in your accounting house

00:25.393 --> 00:27.092
Is enough to prove
your guilt.

00:27.094 --> 00:30.095
You may keep your life,
but that is all you may keep.

00:31.097 --> 00:33.165
