00:37.103 --> 00:38.103
(laughs)

00:38.105 --> 00:40.105
You didn't say the race was

00:40.107 --> 00:42.107
Starting from
the bottom of the hill.

00:42.109 --> 00:45.144
It isn't very sporting
to just sit down, is it?

00:45.146 --> 00:47.146
Hurry up, missus.

00:47.148 --> 00:49.281
Isn't this
what husbands are for?

00:49.283 --> 00:51.116
Or servants?

00:51.118 --> 00:53.318
