38:59.071 --> 39:01.604
â™ª blue skies

39:01.606 --> 39:04.808
â™ª I need a little sunshine...

39:04.810 --> 39:06.543
Francis.

39:06.545 --> 39:08.511
Uh, the baby's sleeping, but...

39:08.513 --> 39:09.779
I was looking for you.

39:11.682 --> 39:13.750
You said that you missed
our friendship,

39:13.752 --> 39:16.453
Our closeness.

39:16.455 --> 39:18.722
It was a loss for me, too.

39:18.724 --> 39:20.924
I'd like us to
be close again.

39:20.926 --> 39:22.926
Friends.

39:24.028 --> 39:25.128
(baby groans)

39:25.130 --> 39:26.629
Family, as it were.

39:26.631 --> 39:29.132
I'd like that.

39:29.134 --> 39:33.470
â™ª I just want
to hold your hand â™ª

39:33.472 --> 39:36.673
â™ª oh, you know
when you're alone â™ª

39:36.675 --> 39:39.943
â™ª I'm holding on

39:39.945 --> 39:41.745
â™ª oh, oh

39:41.747 --> 39:43.146
(quiet laugh)

39:43.148 --> 39:45.081
â™ª oh, you know when you're...

39:45.083 --> 39:46.516
That feeling.

39:46.518 --> 39:49.986
Your heart opening
alongside his hand.

39:49.988 --> 39:53.089
Isn't it extraordinary?

39:53.091 --> 39:56.726
Yes, it is.

39:56.728 --> 40:00.463
â™ª your soul...

40:03.067 --> 40:04.934
Mary.

40:04.936 --> 40:07.804
Please, let me speak.

40:07.806 --> 40:09.973
I knew I was taking
advantage of you,

40:09.975 --> 40:11.975
Your regard for me, and you
deserve better than that.

40:11.977 --> 40:14.711
It's done now.
No need to apologize again.

40:14.713 --> 40:17.113
I am sorry, but I'm
not here to apologize.

40:17.115 --> 40:20.150
I'm here to tell you the truth.

40:20.152 --> 40:22.185
Which I suppose I already did.

40:22.187 --> 40:24.020
Even before I even realized it.

40:24.022 --> 40:25.522
When I told you to call

40:25.524 --> 40:27.957
Things off with lola.

40:27.959 --> 40:30.860
I didn't want to lose you.

40:30.862 --> 40:32.862
Not to another or to...

40:32.864 --> 40:35.432
To the charges of treason.

40:35.434 --> 40:38.935
I imagined you dead.

40:38.937 --> 40:42.005
That loss and your
betrayal pained me

40:42.007 --> 40:43.973
